'''Spidersloths''' were massive, arboreal predators indigenous to the jungles of [[Tenupe]]. They had multiple [[Limb/Legends|legs]], prehensile tails, and shaggy fur.

One such creature bit [[Alema Rar]] almost in half during her duel with [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] in the [[Battle of Tenupe]], [[36 ABY]]. Alema was believed [[Death/Legends|dead]], but she returned alive four [[Standard year/Legends|years]] later, heavily disfigured.

